# LibrePGP specification                                   -*- org -*-

* Editing

 The draft document is the librepgp.md file

* Building

Make sure ruby-kramdown-rfc2629 and xml2rfc are installed. Then run

: make

* Publishing

Before uploding to the IETF site rename the generated files:

: mv librepgp.txt draft-xxx-librepgp-nn.txt
: mv librepgp.xml draft-xxx-librepgp-nn.xml
